A cyberpunk-style macro photograph of a half-eaten glossy red apple beside scattered orange carrot sticks on a dark metallic surface, illuminated by harsh neon pink and electric blue lighting. In the blurred background, an abandoned greasy pizza slice sits in shadow, its cheese congealing under flickering holographic ambient light. Steam or vapor rises subtly from the processed food, giving it an ominous, toxic aura, while the fresh produce appears crisp and vibrant with tiny droplets of water catching the neon glow. The scene is set on what appears to be a cluttered hacker's desk with circuit board patterns visible in the reflective surface, creating a moody late-night atmosphere of digital rebellion against industrial food.
